Empty states are displayed when a page has no content.

```jsx
<EmptyState
  {props} defaults={{title: "Clients", icon: "clients", link: "auth0.com"}}
  action={{
    icon: 'plus',
    label: 'Create Client',
    handler: () => {}
  }}
